  "text": "Palliative chemotherapy is considered the standard of care for patients with unresectable tumors. Multi-agent chemotherapy regimens may have a response rate of up to 35 %, but results are rarely durable and long-term survival is rare [CITATION_1] . In these patients, re-irradiation, if applicable,",
